body:
@carpodaster You can tell Google to export either to csv or tsv, but can't define settings.
If there is the `,` symbol in a cell, Google Sheets will put `"` around the value.
E.g. `2017002,JSFoo 2017,"Sep 15, 2017","Sep 16, 2017",Bangalore,India,Asia Pacific,https://jsfoo.in/2017/,,,`
